Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面要讀哪本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間大量的推理小說完好無損地漂流到了島上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有件事我一直想做做看  哪怕就一次也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  就是像推理小說中的主人公那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想試著真正去和怪人決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去解決事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想以此為藍本來寫小說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是清正先生的話應該能寫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定寫一下試試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會期待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我沒有文采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:24.93,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去揭秘吧  偵探（後篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之名為紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話那邀請帖果然是你發的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那綾音所看到的我  也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  百面怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想聽到年輕少女的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看到她們恐怖的表情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在那少女的皮膚上塗了島上最癢的東部森林的山藥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會自然好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過得要一周時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想立刻就治好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用這解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點把那個拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…居然對我重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你作為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要解毒藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在滿月還未消失之前抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做的話  就全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是朔夜小姐把什麼當作敵人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐照顧周到特意為我們放的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊洗澡一邊看煙花也是很享受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是紅夜叉但也是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲開我的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是敵人但也值得欽佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先回月見亭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為事件會就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人好遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要泡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得大家都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天馬上就要過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的樂趣現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是馬上要睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴真是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上不單單只是睡覺的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整晚努力的修行也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凜到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶行人大人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他睡在同一被窩裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一整晚在裡面卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡覺技能的特訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍  我覺得不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  大姐頭不能偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想…想和公子…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說很大膽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  行人和我同一個房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起睡的應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴不是每晚都睡一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  讓我們一晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在還沒出嫁之前女孩子怎麼就能做出這樣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還是未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話真是沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡輪到我出場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你淺薄的智慧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正起不到什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  在行人洗澡回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先回自己的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後只剩下給行人的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…要寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想與你一起共渡良宵  請來我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  讓行人自己來選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是挑戰書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也許行人會誰都不選獨自一人去空房間睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓它們去空房間待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等行人來了把他趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人最喜歡的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切將在今晚揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼  當然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  也許是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜才不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照其行動規律來看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會假扮成某人然後混到大家裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窺視等待引發下次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼的話  請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否是假貨  我會識破他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真不愧是科學的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼特殊的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  只是想一個一個扯她們的臉來確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐要是去扯的話  就算是真的皮膚也會扯掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐傷害了客人  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼原始的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有更加科學性的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據紅外線透視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據聲紋和體溫的個體識別之類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能有那麼便利的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是SF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(SF：Science  Fiction  超現實的作品)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為朔夜小姐的存在本身已經是SF了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡不能依靠科學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠直接的方法來把他逼到絕境了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  對偵探來說最大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是頂頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(頂頭：相撲和摔跤的格鬥手段之一，用自己的頭部頂向對手進行攻擊)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用頭腦  也就是推理力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧  紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受這挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來…不會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是練習  練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能在公子面前太隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得稍微注重下儀表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了的話玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  已經看過信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人所在的地方  會是誰的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是宮本武藏打倒佐佐木小次郎時的戰法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁心智混亂之時忽然閃現一口氣決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會上當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了尖叫  過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師…傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是因為激烈的按摩而動彈不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼按摩會那麼激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來曾有什麼人在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類按摩椅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰會做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是紅夜叉  千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  真正的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那邀請帖是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才綾音犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍就是第二個犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去  就會出現第三  第四個犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你擅自妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和行人單獨兩人渡過一夜的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會這樣撲過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後奇癢無比  難過死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手卻夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  再下面點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音皮膚真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因為太癢而進入了妄想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也許會稍微輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉那傢伙接下來打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新的犧牲者出現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點阻止的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅梅小姐的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼沾在臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道又是山藥汁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  身體有什麼地方癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…梅梅你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…雖然還不值得誇耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  忽然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是平常害羞的梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:34.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓行人大人看到害羞的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那孩子所塗的不是山藥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那孩子塗的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦沾到便會立即想做H的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘑菇泥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然解毒藥在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來少年也不是不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅拜託你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:13:59.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不使用這發笑的藥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回不讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  就是這個狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  剛才開始就那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個敏捷的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  是凜的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼回來這裡  命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為姐姐不帶我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  你選擇我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像大叔一樣的毫無疑問是真正的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那樣的話只能一個個找了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由就被打出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜這樣打了她一下就讓她睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才上面有可疑的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  在二樓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  還醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是看了信而過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我放心了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最喜歡的人是小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等  行人你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧  怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給你看證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才所說的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴的話  能分清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟每天都一起生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個行人  和平常的感覺有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  仔細看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止  離開小鈴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺…殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…這時候一般應該互相證明自己是真的才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰理你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點玩過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經窮途末路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在小說裡不清楚你是誰就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我會在這裡揭穿你的真實面目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒有注意到被引誘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有懼高症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然怕的動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前邀請來的男人還能再稍微有點樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對做不到像那個男人那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許…說絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如傳言中那樣是個很有趣的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得那孩子會如此中意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得湧出了創作欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…總有一天會在滿月之時再會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓他跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑那麼點洞察力就像揭穿我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他不服輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面時還是小心點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時是會使用忍者招術的怪人紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時以那事件為基礎而寫小說神秘的作家靜丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過其真實身份是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這試煉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如千影所說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合第二代主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然怪人的宿敵就該是擁有強烈的不服輸精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能看到靜丸的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的讀者都會非常高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過無論怎麼說  已經約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會再次寫新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和靜丸最重要的書迷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演紅夜叉並開始寫小說的契機是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了引起那位喜歡推理小說的書迷的注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經早上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是不知道行人選擇了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是有點遺憾卻又松了一口氣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  我們噩夢般的一晚結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  紅夜叉的犧牲者太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉  這憤怒總有一天會償還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  要揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:11.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月見亭的殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己作為小說的原型  心情好複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且話說回來靜丸到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道  是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘還是保持那神秘比較好  這才是推理小說的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅夜叉也是  靜丸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及女人也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
